==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: mull over
<hw>mull over</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To think about; to consider;
to ruminate about; <as>as, <ex>mull</ex> it <ex>over</ex> and decide in
the morning</as>.</def> <mark>[Colloq. U.S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

